|work=[[共同通訊社|共同通訊社]]|date=2007-10-05|language=ja|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222173321/https://www.47news.jp/CN/200710/CN2007100501000306.html|archivedate=2014-02-22|deadurl=yes}}</ref>，而碰巧School Days的此集含有女子高中生的暴力和人性黑暗面的情節，神奈川電視台因避諱而無預先通知地以[[北欧|北欧]][[斯堪的纳维亚|斯堪的纳维亚]]风光片{{notetag|背景音樂《[[G弦上的詠嘆調|G弦上的詠嘆調]]》。}}代替了原先播出的动画，其後[[千葉電視台|千葉電視台]]和[[爱知电视台|爱知电视台]]亦以同樣理由取消了原定的播映计划。[[每日新闻|每日新闻]]和[[日本时报|日本时报]]针对此事进行了报导<ref name="mainichi">{{cite web|url=http://mainichi.jp/enta/mantan/anime/archive/news/2007/09/20070919mog00m200002000c.html|title=Schoolgirl murders father, defers final broadcast of School Days|publisher=[[每日新聞|每日新聞]]|accessdate=2012-01-10|language=ja|date=2007-09-19|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071015145502/http://mainichi.jp/enta/mantan/anime/archive/news/2007/09/20070919mog00m200002000c.html|archivedate=2007-10-15|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref name="japantimes">{{cite web|url=http://www.japantimes.co.jp/text/nn20070919a6.html|title=Teenage girl admits killing dad with ax|publisher=[[The_Japan_Times|The Japan Times]]|accessdate=2012-01-10|date=2007-09-19|archive-date=2012-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121130074021/http://www.japantimes.co.jp/text/nn20070919a6.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而已把年齡對象調整為15歲以上的AT-X則沒有更改<ref name="mainichi"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mainichi-msn.co.jp/entertainment/manga/manganews/news/20070919mog00m200002000c.html |script-title=ja:School Days：京都の父殺害事件で最終回の放送見送る　女子高生の暴力シーンを考慮 |accessdate=2007-09-19 |archive-date=2007-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070926221835/http://www.mainichi-msn.co.jp/entertainment/manga/manganews/news/20070919mog00m200002000c.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.schooldays-anime.com/news/newspup/index.html |script-title=ja:「School Days」12話放送休止に関して |access-date=2007-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071001172621/http://www.schooldays-anime.com/news/newspup/index.html |archive-date=2007-10-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。[[0verflow|0verflow]]在当天通过他们的博客发表致歉声明<ref name="0verflow_topics">{{cite web|url=http://www.0verflow.com/html/topics/index.html|title=Updates: June 1 ~ November 12, 2007|location=Kanda, Chiyoda-ku, Tokyo|publisher=[[0verflow|0verflow]]|date=2007-06-01|accessdate=2012-01-07|language=ja|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080217125225/http://www.0verflow.com/html/topics/index.html|archivedate=2008-02-17|deadurl=yes}}</ref>，并请观众等候再次播放。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.0verflow.com/html/topics/070919_schooldays_12.html|title=About the School Days episode 12 broadcast|location=Kanda, Chiyoda-ku, Tokyo|publisher=[[0verflow|0verflow]]|date=2007-09-19|accessdate=2012-01-10|language=ja|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080217130238/http://www.0verflow.com/html/topics/070919_schooldays_12.html|archivedate=2008-02-17|deadurl=yes}}</ref>在接下来的一周，0verflow宣布它已经安排在9月27日于[[东京动画中心|秋叶原3D剧场]]放映最后一集。希望参加的人必须通过电子邮件注册通行证，满18岁以及携带身份证件和《[[Summer_Days|Summer Days]]》的遊戲軟體。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://12.0verflow.com/|title=School Days TV anime sign-up|location=Kanda, Chiyoda-ku, Tokyo|publisher=[[0verflow|0verflow]]|accessdate=2012-01-13|language=ja|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071014001708/http://12.0verflow.com/|archivedate=2007-10-14|deadurl=yes}}</ref>同一天，AT-X宣布在九月二十七日和十月一日发布未经修改的最终回动画。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.at-x.com/whats_new/detail.html/1291|title=School Days episode 12 broadcast information|publisher=[[AT-X|AT-X]]|date=2007-09-26|language=ja|accessdate=2012-01-13|archive-date=2012-12-17|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Cy3rjR2s?url=http://www.at-x.com/whats_new/detail/1291|dead-url=no}}</ref>

